@startuml nav_eta_to_ibox_zone_distance_route_state_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Nav ETA To IBOX Zone Distance Route State Signal Flow\n(navigation ETA + route activity -> IBOX zone-distance derivation and route-state aggregation)

participant "Nav module bus" as NavMod #F4F7FB
participant "Navigation route bus" as NavRoute #E8F0FE
participant "IBOX\nconnectivity aggregator" as IBOX #E8F7E8
participant "IBOX runtime state" as IboxState #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nroute readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== IBOX Inputs ==

NavMod -> IBOX : frmNavModuleStateMsg\nNavRouteClass / NavGuideType /\nNavEtaMinutes / NavSpeedLimit
NavRoute -> IBOX : frmNavigationRouteMsg\nEtaMinutes
activate IBOX
IBOX -> IBOX : nav freshness windows
IBOX -> IBOX : etaMinutes = Route Eta when fresh,\nelse Nav Eta when fresh
IBOX -> IBOX : deriveZoneDistanceFromEtaMinutes()
IBOX -> IBOX : roadZone = NavRouteClass
IBOX -> IBOX : routeState = 1 when roadZone>0,\n2 when navDirection>0 and zoneDistance>0
note right of IBOX
Representative gating inputs
- NavRouteClass
- NavGuideType
- NavEtaMinutes
- EtaMinutes
end note

== IBOX Runtime Publication ==

IBOX -> IboxState : runtime zoneDistance / routeState /\nroadZone / navDirection
note right of IBOX
Representative outputs
- zoneDistance
- routeState
- roadZone
- navDirection
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

IboxState -> Obs : route-distance visibility /\nroute observers
deactivate IBOX

note over NavMod, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Navigation module and route ETA context reach IBOX
2. IBOX selects the freshest ETA source
3. IBOX derives zone distance from ETA buckets
4. IBOX updates route-state aggregation for downstream readers
end note

@enduml
